-- Anglian Water Said to Hire Banks to Arrange Bond Investor Call
-- B y   H a n n a h   B e n j a m i n
-- 2012-03-19T10:56:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-19/anglian-water-said-to-hire-banks-to-arrange-bond-investor-call.html
Anglian Water Group Ltd. hired
Barclays Capital and  Lloyds Banking Group Plc (LLOY)  to arrange a
conference call with bond investors, according to a banker with
knowledge of the matter. An issue of bonds in pounds may follow
the meeting, the banker said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Hannah Benjamin in London at 
 hbenjamin1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
